Mega Con has come and gone, and it was awesome! Comics were sold, friends were made, and GRWMC was introduced to many new people.
Below this post, you’ll find a photo of the two of us, promoting Giant Robot Warrior Maintenance Crew at Mervyn’s booth. He also did well with selling art prints, and he’s always willing to take on new commissions.
And while we were at Mega Con, we managed to shoot many, many photos of cosplayers, posing with our first issue. You can check them out at our Facebook page here;

Well, it looks like the GRWMC photo contest didn’t really work out. But that’s okay, it was just one more experiment we wanted to try to promote the comic. Other opportunities will come up.
In other news, we now have Giant Robot Warrior Maintenance Crew issue 2 for sale on the Cosmic Times website! Make with the clicky right here;
http://www.cosmictimes.net/grwmc.html
